headline.main: AXIS SEES BRITISH BLOCKED IN LIBYA; Italy Claims Destruction of Armored Brigade -- Denies Fall of Bardia or Gambut

lead_paragraph: ROME, Nov. 25 -- The Italian and German forces were still holding their own last evening at the same key points, in the Libyan battle where fighting has been going on for six days, it was announced in today's Italian war bulletin.
